      "date": "2017-04-04 20:51:15.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\n(3 comments)\n\nMost of my comments on https://review.whamcloud.com/26333 also apply here.\n\nThe main question is whether we need to be able to overload component IDs and flags into the same field or not?  If we don't need to do this for the protocol, then we shouldn't be doing it in the interface.  If we already require this for the protocol then we may as well do the same for the interface since there isn't any benefit to keeping flags and IDs separate.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
